description:
The NDIS has become some what untouchable thanks to media scare tactics.

''I don't think any Government on either side of politics is really suggesting we're going to take money off the you know people with serious disabilities It's the people more at the margin who arguably maybe should be getting other services in the community that we're really talking about'' says John Kehoe

Watch the full video on our YouTube channel.
https://youtu.be/cyw3y83xXxU
